values: I feel sorry for my human. She hasn't been sleeping much. She either feeds us too early or tpp late... it worries me. Last night the people where organizing stuff late into the night. They then woke up early again. Janine didn't feed me untill 10. At least I got fed. Because there this one fish that wont leave me alone and I swear I'm going to kill him.

I don't get why they complain (the two offspring human things and the rest of the humans I kno) about being in skool. I'm alwayz in skool. HELLO!!! Skool of phish. I can't spell well. 

My human woke up early, she did some talk on phone with the other human. I'm not sure who... but yeah. She fed us early too. Whats the rush? I like my breakfast at 7 SHARP!

I need to spell. Maybe I should join there skool of humans?
My name is Bright Eyes... I was not named after the band but for my EYES!!! Gosh! Um... I do like Bright Eyes.

1. Who are you?
2. Are we friends?
3. When and how did we meet?
4. How have I affected you?
5. What do you think of me?
6. What's the fondest memory you have of me?
7. How long do you think we will be friends?
8. Do you love me?
9. Do you have a crush on me?
10. Would you kiss me?
11. Would you hug me?
12. Physically, what stands out?
13. Emotionally, what stands out?
14. Do you wish I was cooler?
15. On a scale of 1-10, how hot am I? 
16. Give me a nickname and explain why you picked it.
17. Am I loveable?
18. How long have you known me?
19. Describe me in one word.
20. What was your first impression?
21. Do you still think that way about me now?
22. What do you think my weakness is?
23. Do you think I'll get married? if yes, who?
24. What makes me happy?
25. What makes me sad?
26. What reminds you of me?
27. If you could give me anything what would it be?
28. How well do you know me?
29. When's the last time you saw me?
30. Ever wanted to tell me something but couldn't?
31. Do you think I could kill someone?
32. Are you going to put this on your LiveJournal and see what I say about you?

So today I didn't do much.  Bo got an LJ and I was quite envious. So I made Janine get me one. HA! She is so under my control! She fed me late today. Damn her! Oh well... Fattie didn't share the flakes again. I wasn't really hungry anyway. I haven't ate well since Carlene died. I loved her. I don't think Janine knew that. Hmm... now she does, because she types this for me!!! MUHAHAHAHAHA!!! Ah, silly human.

SO I got a LJ. It's quite hard to type with fins. So I have my human do that all for me. Um... well for now, I'm making my human also make this nice a pretty. Just like me. Yep. 

So any questions?
